HEADWORD: Disputer
<hw>Dis*put"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who disputes,
or who is given to disputes; a controvertist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Where is the <qex>disputer</qex> of this world?</q> <rj><qau>1
